data_table.description: Clinic Exam Dates, Sex, Age at Exam, Original Exam 1 - Exam 32, Offspring Exam 1 - Exam 9, Generation 3 Exam 1 - Exam 2, New Offspring Spouse Exam 1 - Exam 2, Omni 1 Exam 1 - Exam 4, and Omni 2 Exam 1 - Exam 2. The time interval is from 1948 through 2014. The age at each clinic exam was calculated using the clinic exam date and the date of birth. Clinic exam dates were calculated using the number of days between exam 1 and subsequent exams.

variable.comment: Date includes month, day and year, however coding manual displays only month and year to preserve confidentiality. Number of days since Exam 1.
